headline: General Mills to Webcast Presentation at CAGNY Conference on Feb. 17, 2026
summary: MINNEAPOLIS, February 02, 2026--General Mills, Inc. (NYSE: GIS) announced today that Chairman and Chief Executive Officer Jeff Harmening, Chief Financial Officer Kofi Bruce, and Group President of North America Retail and North America Pet Dana McNabb will be featured speakers at the Consumer Analyst Group of New York (CAGNY) Conference in Orlando, Florida, on Feb. 17, 2026. A webcast of the live presentation is scheduled to begin at 7 a.m. CT, and a replay of the event will be available at www.
